Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.15,0:00:59.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,HAPPY TOGETHER
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.16,0:01:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,黎耀辉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lai Yiu-Fai...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.00,0:01:12.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不如我们由头再来过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}let's start over.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.84,0:01:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“不如由头来过”这句话何宝荣的口头禅\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ho Po-Wing always says, "Let's start over,"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.51,0:01:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我承认这句话对我很有杀伤力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and it gets to me every time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.05,0:01:22.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们在一起已经很久\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We've been together for a while
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.72,0:01:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,中间也有分开过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and we break up often...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.64,0:01:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是不知为什么每次听见他说这句话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but whenever he says, "Let's start over,"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.10,0:01:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就会跟他再走到一起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I find myself back with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.06,0:01:31.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为想由头来过 我们离开了香港\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In order to start over, we left Hong Kong.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.73,0:01:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,两个人走着走着就来到了阿根廷\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We hit the road and ended up in Argentina.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.10,0:02:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请问瀑布怎么去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Which way to Iguazu?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.77,0:02:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这路不到瀑布\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The waterfall? Iguazu is that way. It's the other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.40,0:03:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又说会看地图 走错路了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Didn't you say you could read a map? We're miles off!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.53,0:03:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走错路需不需要死呢 走错路不就掉头喽\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So what's the big deal? Just turn around and find the right road.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.55,0:03:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,干\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.67,0:03:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,买什么车 搭巴士不是好端端罗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why did we get a car? We should've taken the bus.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.30,0:03:30.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样的废材又开不动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This wreck is useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.76,0:03:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你来开吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.28,0:03:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有废材都好过没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is better than nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.58,0:03:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在很多身家咩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're not rich.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.54,0:03:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有架车给你坐都好过挤巴士啊 三十多个钟头\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And who wants to be stuck in a bus for 30 hours?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.21,0:03:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,旅行是这样的啦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But that's what traveling is about!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.17,0:04:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没想着这样子的啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not for me it isn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.05,0:04:09.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下去推推车啊 谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get out and push, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.73,0:05:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,初初来到阿根廷什么地方也不认识\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When we first got here, we had no idea where to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.52,0:05:05.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一天何宝荣买了一盏枱灯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then Po-Wing bought a lamp
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.65,0:05:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得很漂亮\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and I really liked it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.11,0:05:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们很想知道灯罩上面的瀑布在哪里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We wanted to find the waterfall on the lamp.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.82,0:05:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,问了很多人才知道是Iguazu\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We found out it was at Iguazu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.11,0:05:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本来想着去了瀑布就回香港\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We planned to see it and then go home
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.28,0:05:16.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,结果我们迷了路\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but we lost our way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.17,0:05:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.34,0:05:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你去哪儿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.83,0:06:06.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其实到现在我都没搞清楚那天我们去了哪里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I never did find out where we were that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.09,0:06:10.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只记得他跟我说 和我在一起的日子好闷\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He said being with me is a bore,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.76,0:06:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不如大家分开一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that we should take a break...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.80,0:06:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有机会遇回再由头来过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and perhaps start over again some day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.51,0:06:18.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其实何宝荣的"由头来过"可以有两个意思\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"Starting over" means different things to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.95,0:08:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在阿根廷找工作不是那么容易 因为这里不是很多中国人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's hard to find work in Argentina. There aren't a lot of Chinese around.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.87,0:08:07.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟他分开后我来到布宜洛斯艾利斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}After we broke up, I came to Buenos Aires.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.71,0:08:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在一间探戈酒吧当接待\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've been working as a doorman at a tango bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.00,0:08:12.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走开啦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Move it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.21,0:08:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎 欢迎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.84,0:08:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请进 请进\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.88,0:08:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎 欢迎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.42,0:08:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请大家快点啦 快点 快点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go right on in!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.43,0:08:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎 欢迎 欢迎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Welcome! Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.05,0:08:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎 欢迎 欢迎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Welcome! Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.22,0:08:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请进 请进\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This way! This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.77,0:08:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,里面坐 里面坐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Take a seat inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.99,0:10:47.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那晚我又碰见何宝荣 我没想过要跟他由头来过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Seeing him again,I realize I don't want to "start over."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.57,0:10:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想回香港\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I just want to go back to Hong Kong.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.25,0:10:57.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要来玩吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You coming to the game?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.38,0:11:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样 你应该来 我跟那家伙都在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How about it? You should come. I'll be here with the guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.21,0:11:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辉 你有电话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fai, telephone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.30,0:11:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我 -电话来个不停\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Me? -They can't keep calling like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.27,0:11:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.81,0:11:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你找我干嘛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.47,0:11:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跑来跑去怎么拍\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I said stand still!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.15,0:12:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笑嘛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Smile!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.57,0:12:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,干 不拍了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fuck it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.05,0:12:28.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这么久\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}hey why take you so long
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.01,0:12:29.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,烟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}cigarette
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.84,0:12:30.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,的士\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Taxi
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.93,0:12:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给我火\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}give me a light
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.47,0:12:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给我个火\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}give me light
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.55,0:13:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 谁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hello ? Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.26,0:13:14.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辉 有电话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fai! Telephone!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.27,0:13:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.02,0:13:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.77,0:13:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is me
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.48,0:13:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么知道我电话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How did you get my number?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.62,0:13:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开门呀 何宝荣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ho Po-Wing, open the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.04,0:13:41.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开门\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Open the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.84,0:13:48.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样啊 黎耀辉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's up, Lai Yiu-Fai?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.51,0:13:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样 何宝荣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's up, Ho Po-Wing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.30,0:13:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,进来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.35,0:13:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我干嘛要进来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why should I?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.81,0:13:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有话跟你说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I want to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.39,0:14:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什么在这儿说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We can talk here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.93,0:14:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有要紧的跟你说 进来啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's important. Come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.32,0:14:07.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什么快点讲啦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.15,0:14:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛呀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.20,0:14:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说完啦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.07,0:14:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有啦 走呀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You can go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.91,0:14:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走呀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.54,0:14:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别推我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't push me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.04,0:14:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,推我我揍你的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll hit you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.38,0:14:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,揍我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.76,0:14:31.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你妈的有种就捏死我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Kill me if you got the balls!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.97,0:14:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仆街仔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You little shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.10,0:14:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我仆街得过你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You think you're any better?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.85,0:14:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“晚安晚安请进请进”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"Welcome! Welcome! Come in! Come in!"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.65,0:14:47.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做什么鸟不去做鸭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Isn't that prostitution?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.32,0:14:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你理我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's none of your business!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.53,0:14:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不像你 有鬼佬照顾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not like you have white trash taking care of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.99,0:14:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,照你老妈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fuck you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.70,0:14:56.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我什么都没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm broke!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.57,0:14:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,钱又被你花光了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You blew all my money!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.41,0:15:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还要回香港\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I want to go back to Hong Kong.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.37,0:15:02.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没钱怎么回\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How can I with no money?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.54,0:15:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不想做啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You think I like that job?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.01,0:15:21.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有没有后悔跟我一起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you regret being with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.60,0:15:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好他妈后悔啊我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You damn well bet I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.89,0:15:26.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没见你之前我一点也不后悔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I had no regrets till I met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.65,0:15:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在我他妈的后悔得要死\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now my regrets could kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.24,0:15:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.78,0:15:36.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎样啦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.78,0:15:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,示威 在奚落我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You trying to put me down?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.16,0:15:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我你混得很好啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Showing me you're well off?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.12,0:15:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你混得好关我鸟事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't give a shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.83,0:15:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你叫我来干嘛 叫我来干嘛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why did you ask me to come?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.38,0:15:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想你陪我一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I just want to be with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.59,0:15:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我好想你陪我一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I really do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.80,0:16:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.59,0:16:32.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.01,0:16:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不喜欢就卖掉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sell it if you don't like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.01,0:16:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,干\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.51,0:17:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又怎么啦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What is it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.85,0:17:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可不可以先把表还我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can I have the watch back?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.90,0:17:35.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坐后面啦 后面没这么光\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's sit in the back. It's darker.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.40,0:17:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛 我现在见不得人啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You don't want to be seen with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.78,0:17:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得自己的样子很见得人啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not with your face looking like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.24,0:17:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看到的咩 我以为你看不见喎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So you can see! I didn't think you'd noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.58,0:17:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,整天一声不响 我以为你没察觉喎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You didn't say anything. I thought you couldn't see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.46,0:17:53.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来你看到我被人打的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So you noticed I got beaten up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.71,0:17:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想我讲什么 不打也被人打了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What do you want me to say? What happened happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.63,0:18:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂大佬 一场朋友啊你都问候一句吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're friends, aren't we? Couldn't you say something nice?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.76,0:18:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我这么大第一次被人打都是因为你啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It happened because of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.80,0:18:07.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别说为了我 别赖得就赖\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't blame it on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.22,0:18:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没说要那只手表 你要拿给我而已\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I didn't ask for that watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.72,0:18:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你又收下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But you took it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.89,0:18:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你应该当面给回我吖嘛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You could've given it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.44,0:18:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当面给回我我怎会被人打\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then I wouldn't have gotten beat up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.36,0:18:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是想被人打多一顿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You want some more?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.79,0:18:33.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不要我陪你回去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Want me to take you home?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.33,0:18:34.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,省点啦你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't bother!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.04,0:18:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只晓得欺负我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're always bullying me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.86,0:19:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂你家呢 你家在哪边\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You live here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.19,0:19:02.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在这儿等我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.12,0:19:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给回你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.96,0:19:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.75,0:19:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.71,0:19:22.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给支烟来吸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Got a cigarette?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.98,0:19:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,火呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A light?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.62,0:19:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以后别再找我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't come looking for me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.77,0:21:04.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 是 辉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hello ? Yes, Fai ?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.27,0:21:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他不久前走开了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He left a while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.61,0:21:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不久前而已\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It was a while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.07,0:21:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不客气 再见\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sure. Don't mention it. Bye. See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.21,0:21:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,黎耀辉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lai Yiu-Fai!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.22,0:22:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,黎耀辉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lai Yiu-Fai...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.18,0:22:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不如我们由头来过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}let's start over.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.02,0:23:43.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这儿都几好呀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is a nice place.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.52,0:23:47.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住了多久\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How long have you lived here?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.69,0:23:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,几个月\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A few months.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.61,0:23:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么住得这么偏\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's not exactly centrally located.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.82,0:23:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,便宜点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's cheap.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.82,0:23:56.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.74,0:24:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天花板很高看 出去风景也不错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nice high ceiling. Good view outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.29,0:24:08.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这灯你没丢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You still have that lamp?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.96,0:24:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以为早给你抛了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I thought you'd have thrown it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.13,0:24:18.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你最终有没有去看瀑布\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did you ever get to see the falls?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.30,0:24:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有 你呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.18,0:24:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.18,0:24:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等你嘛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.98,0:24:30.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,待我好了我们一起去好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We'll go when I'm better.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.48,0:24:31.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到时候再说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We'll see.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.73,0:24:33.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今晚你睡这边\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sleep here tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.82,0:24:35.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-那你呢 -我睡沙发\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-What about you ? -I'll take the sofa.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.03,0:26:02.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎 欢迎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.54,0:26:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎 欢迎 里面坐 里面坐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Welcome.Welcome.Come in
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.25,0:26:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好很好 再来一张\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Good. Let's do one more.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.42,0:26:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,低一点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lower a bit
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.67,0:26:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三 笑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}One, two, three, smile!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.97,0:26:26.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,近一点 近一点啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Closer together now.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.68,0:26:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一 二 三 好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}One, two, three. Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.64,0:26:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.81,0:27:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你什么都不做只会吃 滚开啦 -好啦 好啦!\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-You do nothing but eat! Scram! -Okay, okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.46,0:27:36.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,何宝荣 吃饭啦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, Ho Po-Wing. Let's eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.79,0:27:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃饭啦 起来吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get up and eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.59,0:27:51.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夹块鸡来尝下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Give me some chicken.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.40,0:28:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是不是很脏啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Am I very dirty?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.49,0:28:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,医生说不能洗澡嘛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The doctor said no showers.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.83,0:28:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么多咬痕的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What are all these bites?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.41,0:28:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大哥你张床几多蚤子啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your bed has fleas!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.37,0:28:20.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下雨嘛 一下雨总是这样子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's what happens when it rains.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.34,0:28:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好天气时嗮下床盖啊 被单吖嘛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When the weather's better, you should disinfect the bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.51,0:28:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咬死人咩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't want to get bitten to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.97,0:28:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抬高手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lift your arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.35,0:28:38.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂痛啊我的手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, that hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.40,0:28:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-肉来的 -又说脏了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Be gentle. -You said you were dirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.32,0:28:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吖嘛 抬得那么高\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're scrubbing too hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.91,0:28:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也喷下那边啦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Spray over there too.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.34,0:29:06.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自己睡那边的嘛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Spray where you sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.19,0:29:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-干什么 -有没烟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-What? -Cigarettes.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.40,0:29:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那边不是还有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.61,0:29:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都他妈的没了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're all gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.82,0:29:28.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-下去给你买 -不用了 睡觉啦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-I'll go buy some. -Don't bother. Go to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.17,0:29:51.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-给我两包香烟 -好的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Give me two packs. -Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.64,0:29:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-谢谢 -再见\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Thank you. -Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.07,0:30:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 干嘛有床不睡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What are you doing? You got your own bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.86,0:30:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I like it like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.16,0:30:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不觉得两个人睡一张沙发很挤\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The sofa's too small for two.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.91,0:30:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不觉得 这样蛮舒服啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. I think it's quite comfy.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.46,0:30:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛咬我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why did you bite me?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.55,0:30:29.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我饿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.59,0:30:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是要睡沙发\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You want this sofa?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.43,0:30:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,干什么呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.97,0:30:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-那我睡床了 -别说这么多话睡觉啦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Fine, I'll take the bed. -Just go back to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.72,0:30:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不你睡床上我睡沙发\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you want the bed, I'll stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.02,0:30:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别像八婆似的好不好啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Quit whining, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.69,0:30:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-喂 -OK 我睡床\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Hey! -Okay, I'll sleep on the bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.37,0:31:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是那么没人情味\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why can't you be nice?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.67,0:31:06.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都说很挤罗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The bed's too small.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.42,0:31:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么挤呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.21,0:31:10.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我睡你上边这样就不挤\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can sleep on top of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.17,0:31:12.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样子睡 这样子睡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We can sleep like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.59,0:31:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是睡床上啊嗱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So you're gonna sleep on the bed?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.26,0:31:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是真这样子对我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't be like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.72,0:31:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,干什么嘛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.77,0:31:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就这样子睡啦 好不好啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's sleep like this, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.06,0:31:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 你睡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay, let's go to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.32,0:31:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别动 大家这样睡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stop tossing around. We'll sleep like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.99,0:31:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你别搞我 -谁搞你 你别搞我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-You better not touch me. -Me touch you? You better not touch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.62,0:31:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,睡觉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Good night. Let's sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.46,0:31:47.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别搞啊 手痛啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Watch my hand. It hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.84,0:31:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老板\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.68,0:32:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给我个意大利千酪比萨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Gimme a mozzarella pizza.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.89,0:32:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那不勒斯比萨饼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Neapolitan?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.18,0:32:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-意大利干酪 -那不勒斯比萨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Mozzarella. -Neapolitan?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.10,0:32:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 意大利干酪比萨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, mozzarella.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.27,0:32:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-意大利干酪 -对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Mozzarella? -Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.73,0:32:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点啦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Move it, fatty!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.07,0:32:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,介绍中国女生给我认识\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Find me a Chinese girl
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.53,0:32:15.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我请你吃 -拿来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-and I'll deliver for free. -Give it here!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.91,0:32:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要爆乳的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I want one with big tits!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.95,0:32:24.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,觉不觉得有什么不同\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Notice anything different?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.04,0:32:32.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真是警告你 别再耍花样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm warning you, no more of your games.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.30,0:32:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-喂 顶不顺了 -什么顶不顺了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-I can't take it anymore! -Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.85,0:32:46.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走一下啦 整天困在那里 蛇都死啦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Keep moving! Morning exercise is good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.39,0:32:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好冷啊 以后再来啦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's cold. Let's do this tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.35,0:32:52.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冷什么呢 神经 走一下啦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's not that cold. Keep moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.41,0:33:03.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-不过又真的好冷嗬 -那怎么样啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-You're right, it's freezing. -Now what?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.12,0:33:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啦 回去啦 回去啦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay, let's go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.83,0:33:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,干\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.17,0:33:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,黎耀辉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lai Yiu-Fai?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.67,0:33:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么啦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How do you feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.22,0:33:21.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好辛苦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.39,0:33:25.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇真的好烫\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're burning up.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.85,0:33:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然烫\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Of course I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.35,0:33:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说你是不是在耍我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What were you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.19,0:33:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天寒地冻的 有觉不睡走去晨运\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why did you drag me out in the cold? It was freezing.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.11,0:33:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么知道你这么弱 走两步你就病了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I never thought a little jog would make you sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.49,0:33:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样啊 起不起得到床啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can you get up?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.45,0:33:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,起不起得到床又怎样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What for?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.79,0:33:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,煮饭罗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To cook something.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.41,0:33:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我肚子好饿啊 我两天没吃东西了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm starving. I haven't eaten for two days!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.46,0:33:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就快饿死啦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm starving to death!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.63,0:33:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是人来的 你问下你自己\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you not human or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.51,0:34:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,病到这样叫我起身煮饭给你吃\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You ask a sick man to cook for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.04,0:34:29.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你妈的 快上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Faster, you son of a bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.89,0:34:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发达了今天\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're rich!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.89,0:34:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,票呢票呢票呢 收钱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where's the ticket? I'll claim the money!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.66,0:35:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.95,0:35:12.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咖啡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.79,0:35:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这步吖嘛 每次总是忘记这一步\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You keep forgetting that step.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.54,0:35:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自己先练习一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Try it by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.63,0:35:23.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成天都不记得上一步\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You keep forgetting that last step.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.10,0:35:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,交叉转那边你到这边做什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Cross your feet and go the other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.60,0:35:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以啦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.73,0:35:38.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.90,0:35:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里试一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay, try it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.99,0:35:50.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}One...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.16,0:35:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,二\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Two...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.04,0:35:53.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Three...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.41,0:35:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,四\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Four...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.21,0:35:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.77,0:37:39.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 我们走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.14,0:37:42.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别说了 我们回家吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stop it, let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.81,0:37:46.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.82,0:37:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们会过得很好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We'll have a good time.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.23,0:38:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.21,0:38:49.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 这么巧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.17,0:38:50.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上街呀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You out for a walk?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.59,0:38:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在等你下班啊傻佬\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was waiting for you, silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.55,0:38:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 怎么不通知一声\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, why didn't you tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.93,0:39:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,通知一声什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tell you what?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.31,0:39:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打电话去你旧公司 说你没有做了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I called you at work. They said you'd quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.44,0:39:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不通知一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You didn't say a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.73,0:39:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不做了有什么好说的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's there to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.03,0:39:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你是不是打得他很惨了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did you hurt him bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.78,0:39:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不讲啦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not telling you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.45,0:39:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讲啦 你不讲我睡不着觉的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on! I won't be able to sleep if you don't tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.20,0:39:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,睡不着就上街喽 你这么喜欢上街\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then go for a stroll. You like going out.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.62,0:39:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 那我睡不着你也睡不着是不是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If I don't sleep, you don't sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.33,0:39:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你上了街我怎么会睡不着 -说来听听呀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-I'll sleep fine if you're out walking. -Why won't you tell me? Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.21,0:39:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-不说 -讲啦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-No. -Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.13,0:39:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不讲啊 好烦啊你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No! You're so annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.18,0:39:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 辉啊 -什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Fai! -What?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.72,0:39:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 咖啡杯没了快点 -哦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-We're out of coffee cups, quick! -Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.61,0:39:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-面啊 -OK 弄多两杯咖啡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Noodles! -All right. Two more cups of coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.07,0:39:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,单听声音就知道这是个厨房\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You can tell it's a kitchen by the noise.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.28,0:40:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你听得仔细一点你就可以分得出来 哪些人在吵架哪些人在炒菜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Listen carefully and you can hear who's cooking and who's just cursing.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.16,0:40:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人在讲电话 有人在洗碗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Some are talking on the phone. Some are washing dishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.42,0:40:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我问你在做什么啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.96,0:40:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃了东西没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Have you eaten?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.92,0:40:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我问你吃了东西没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I said have you eaten yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.84,0:40:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打包回来给你吃罗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll bring something back for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.18,0:40:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想吃什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What do you want to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.81,0:40:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别玩啦 想吃什么啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't play games.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.85,0:40:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你买什么我吃什么罗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just tell me. Whatever you bring is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.64,0:40:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就这样子吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay. Ciao.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.77,0:40:34.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个人很喜欢讲电话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This guy loves talking on the phone...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.78,0:40:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听得出来他的语气很愉快\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and his voice always sounds pleasant.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.86,0:40:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对方一定是他喜欢的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He must be talking to someone he likes.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.34,0:40:59.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还没走啊 其他人都收工了 明天再洗啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Everyone's gone. Finish that tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.47,0:41:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说其他人已经收工了 明天再洗啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I said leave it for tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.22,0:41:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正我没地方去先弄完\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's okay. I have nothing else to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.77,0:41:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是来玩的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Aren't you here on vacation?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.65,0:41:12.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,钱花完了 先赚钱呐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, but I ran out of money.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.86,0:41:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃不吃\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You want some?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.82,0:41:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.53,0:41:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用钱的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.57,0:41:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.12,0:41:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好不好吃\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.59,0:41:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吃\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.09,0:41:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你慢慢吃 我走先\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Enjoy it. I'm going.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.18,0:41:43.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走啦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.66,0:42:04.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辉 打麻将吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fai, wanna play mahjong?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.78,0:42:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别搞我 你们自己玩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, count me out. You guys have fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.29,0:42:14.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,数目不对吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Pay's not right?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.75,0:42:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有啊 算算还要待多久\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, just figuring out how long I have to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.30,0:42:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这边用钱好贵\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Things are pricey here.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.89,0:42:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在看地图啊 去哪里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You reading a map? Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.56,0:42:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想着去瀑布玩一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I want to see the falls.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.81,0:42:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好玩啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's a fun place.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.18,0:42:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你去过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Have you been there?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.48,0:42:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-没有啊 -没去过又说好玩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-No. -Then how do you know it's fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.94,0:42:37.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-就是没有去过才好玩嘛 你一个人去啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Anywhere new is fun. You going alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.59,0:42:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}With a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.69,0:42:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好羡慕你噢 我都不知道在这边要待多久\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I envy you. Looks like I'm stuck here.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.20,0:42:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想去哪儿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where do you want to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.57,0:42:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道啊 能走多远就走多远\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't know. As far as I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.33,0:42:47.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你家人不理你吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Doesn't your family worry?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.83,0:42:50.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我自己出来的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm here on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.54,0:42:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们也不知道我在哪里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They don't know where I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.92,0:42:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想过要回去吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Planning to go back?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.46,0:42:59.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不开心才出来的嘛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I left 'cause I wasn't happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.67,0:43:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有想通以前回去也没什么意思啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I need to figure things out before I go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.09,0:43:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不跟你讲啦 你玩得开心啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Enough about that. Have a good time.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.98,0:43:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是不行 今天好旺啊 明天先吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can't. We're really busy. How about tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.69,0:43:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,星期三不是更好 看戏便宜一半\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Movies are half price on Wednesday.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.36,0:43:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在怎么请假\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can't take a day off!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.16,0:43:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿辉 赶快帮我拿三个鸡蛋过来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fai, bring me three eggs!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.04,0:43:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦 你等等\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hang on.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.67,0:43:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.13,0:43:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找你的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.17,0:43:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 同事罢了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hello? That was a coworker.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.89,0:43:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回来再跟你说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We'll talk when I get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.80,0:43:50.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我工作先了再见\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've got to go. Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.97,0:43:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,忙死了你还在打电话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're busy and you're on the phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.45,0:44:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-干嘛啊你 一大早弄醒人 -你翻我东西干嘛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-What's the matter with you? -You were going through my stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.12,0:44:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我干嘛翻你东西 你神经病啊你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why would I? Are you nuts?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.16,0:44:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没翻我东西我柜子会这么乱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My drawer's a mess!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.50,0:44:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你看看我的手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look at my hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.21,0:44:22.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的手这样拿什么翻 用口翻啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You think I did it with my mouth?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.84,0:44:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再搞我东西 我打断你的腿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do it again and I'll break your legs!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.92,0:44:26.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打呀有种你打呀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fine! Go ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.18,0:44:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来去手没有了 连脚也不要啦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then they'll match my hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.60,0:44:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神经病 我翻你柜子不如翻你衣柜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Think I went through your closet too?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.52,0:44:35.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要再碰我东西就滚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you do it again, you can just get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.77,0:44:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你说的叫我滚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You mean it?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.60,0:44:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来替我穿裤子穿鞋子 我现在滚 来呀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Help me get dressed. I'll leave now!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.69,0:44:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你舍得滚你舍得滚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You will?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.53,0:44:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-滚了睡街上 -我宁愿睡街上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-You'll be sleeping on the street! -I'd rather sleep on the street!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.15,0:44:47.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你别不舍得\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't you regret it!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.91,0:44:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神经病\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lunatic!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.98,0:45:22.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他泡你的 还是你泡他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did he pick you up or did you pick him up?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.23,0:45:26.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-有没有什么 -什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Did you do it? -What?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.57,0:45:29.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你晓得我说什么 -什么啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-You know what. -What?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.66,0:45:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.87,0:45:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.16,0:45:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你管得了我 你没跟别人睡过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's it to you? Haven't you slept with other guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.13,0:45:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么以后你别问我 我也别问你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fine. You don't ask me, and I won't ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.10,0:46:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-喂 -你别再来看我揍你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stay away! I'll beat you up!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.35,0:46:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-可以可以 -过那边睡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Okay, okay. -Sleep over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.11,0:46:07.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,火气这么大啊近来嘛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You get so touchy sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.65,0:46:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,问少少东西而已 不是心中有鬼不就告诉我罗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was just gonna ask if there was something on your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.20,0:46:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么燥\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why are you in such a bad mood?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.83,0:46:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-起身 -干什么啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Get up! -What now? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.41,0:46:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又说要睡觉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Didn't you want to sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.71,0:46:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么喜欢问问题嘛 那么有兴趣知道我的事情嘛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Since you're so fond of questions...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.55,0:46:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我现在想知道你跟什么人睡过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}tell me who you've slept with!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.67,0:46:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像是我先问你跟他有没有睡过 你怎么问我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I believe I asked first. Why are you asking me?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.34,0:46:34.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢烦我嘛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now it's my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.76,0:46:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我现在想知道你跟哪些人睡过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who have you slept with?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.56,0:46:41.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你真要知道 -说呀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-You want to know? -Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.02,0:46:44.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 现在三点半\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's already half past three.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.44,0:46:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我男朋友多过天上繁星\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've had so many boyfriends,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.77,0:46:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我怕讲到九点半你上班我还没讲完\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'd still be counting when you leave for work.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.69,0:46:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无所谓 我现在睡不着\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't mind. I'm not sleepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.78,0:46:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说啊 慢慢说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Take your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.24,0:46:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不喜欢说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.08,0:46:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你这个死家伙 -喂喂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-You little slut! -Hey! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.41,0:47:01.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,够了喎 够了喎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stop it! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.04,0:47:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你滚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.87,0:47:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,认真的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You mean it?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.34,0:47:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-没空跟你开玩笑 -别碰我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Yes, I mean it. -Okay! Don't touch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.55,0:47:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我自己走 -自己走呀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-I'll go! -Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.51,0:47:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打得我那么重 明知道我残废掉还要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know I'm injured and you're giving me bruises.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.81,0:47:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走啦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.18,0:47:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,整晚没得睡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can't get any sleep around here!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.06,0:47:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冷死你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go on and freeze to death!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.15,0:47:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 多少次啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, how many times?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.70,0:47:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说嘛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.29,0:47:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么多少次\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How many times what?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.21,0:47:47.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你跟他做了多少次\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How many times did you two do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.42,0:47:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做得出不怕认嘛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you did it, admit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.21,0:47:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很多次 满意了吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A lot. All right?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.30,0:47:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有跟谁呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Were there others?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.55,0:48:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,楼下保安的有没有啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did you do the janitor downstairs?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.85,0:48:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.15,0:48:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.00,0:48:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还要做多久\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Will it take much longer?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.00,0:49:14.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是辉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is Fai.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.59,0:49:16.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,何宝荣先生在不在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is Mr. Ho Po-Wing there?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.43,0:49:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 拜拜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you. Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.85,0:50:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么黑也不开灯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's so dark. Why don't you turn the light on?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.90,0:51:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去哪儿了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.20,0:51:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,买烟罗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Buying cigarettes.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.03,0:51:07.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,穿得那么漂亮去买烟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All dressed up?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.91,0:51:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,经常都不上街 穿好一点下去逛逛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't get out often, so I dress up when I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.19,0:51:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,买那么多烟干嘛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why did you buy so many?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.86,0:51:47.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,路过就买 免得你半夜跑去买\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To save you from having to go out for them at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.19,0:52:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到哪儿去了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:00.44,0:53:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,横坚闲着 就下街走走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For a walk. I was bored.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.73,0:53:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃宵夜吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Want some food?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:08.03,0:53:09.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得很闷\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you really bored here?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.53,0:53:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是闲着没事找架吵吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do we have to go through this again?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.24,0:53:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我下去走走也不可以\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If I want to go out, I'll go out!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.79,0:53:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.37,0:53:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直都是你喜欢怎么样就怎样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You always do what you like anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.96,0:53:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你今晚是不是睡这边啊 你睡这里的话我睡那边喎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You taking the bed tonight? I'll take the sofa.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.30,0:53:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll take the sofa.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:31.84,0:53:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么知道你回不回来睡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I just wasn't sure you were coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.36,0:53:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃宵夜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.99,0:53:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看着点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.12,0:54:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抢他的球\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get the ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.76,0:54:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,传球\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Pass it.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.93,0:54:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,干\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.39,0:54:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别打架\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Cool it!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.51,0:54:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别打别打\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:17.56,0:54:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,改天再玩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's enough for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:43.81,0:55:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有件事情我一直没说给何宝荣听\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}One thing I never told Ho Po-Wing...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:45.94,0:55:48.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其实我不想他太早复原\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}was that I didn't want him to recover too quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.19,0:55:51.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他受伤的那阵子是我和他最开心的时光\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Those were our happiest days.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:08.31,0:57:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就不能先把房租交了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look, just pay me the rent.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:10.23,0:57:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要干嘛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What do you want? Can't you see I'm cooking?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.15,0:57:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-看不见我在煮菜吗 -煮菜也得交房租\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You still gotta pay the rent!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.53,0:57:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我现在可什么都给不了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can't pay you anything right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:20.91,0:57:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我别的待缴费用还多的是呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not now and that's that.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:57.78,0:57:59.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你拿了我的护照去哪儿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did you take my passport?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:02.53,0:58:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没拿过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:10.50,0:58:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没 没拿我怎么会找不到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No? Then why can't I find it?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:12.46,0:58:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我哪知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:15.38,0:58:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好给回本护照我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Give me back my passport.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:18.42,0:58:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你要护照来干嘛 -你理我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-What do you want it for? -That's none of your business!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:26.10,0:58:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不会还给你的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not giving it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:57.21,0:59:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你想找什么 -你知道我想找什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-What are you looking for? -You know very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.22,0:59:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好拿回出来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:13.81,0:59:15.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要我讲多少次\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How many times do I have to tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.15,0:59:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是不会给回你的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not giving it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:23.53,0:59:25.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来啊 打啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, hit me!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:25.57,0:59:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打啊 打啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hit me! Hit me!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:28.16,0:59:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-打啊 -干\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Hit me! -Fucker!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:51.18,1:01:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天怎么不打麻将\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not playing mahjong today?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:53.76,1:01:55.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不想打就不打\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't feel like it.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:04.86,1:02:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要不要去喝一杯呀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wanna go for a drink?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:11.20,1:02:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别吐嘛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You drank too much.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:13.20,1:02:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走走走 我扶你我扶你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on, let me help you.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:15.41,1:02:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪边\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where's your place?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:09.67,1:03:12.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有没有搞错 这样抱着我怎么打球\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Damn it. Let me go.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:16.72,1:03:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别打架\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No fighting!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:22.81,1:03:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不准用手碰球\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No hands!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:24.44,1:03:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这边\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Over here!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:30.36,1:03:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这边\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Over here!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:49.59,1:03:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨 陪我去看电影\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Want to see a movie with me?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:51.59,1:03:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不看电影 看电影我头痛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't like movies. They give me a headache.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:54.63,1:03:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神经病\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Weirdo.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:57.18,1:03:58.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对 我神经病\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Right, I'm a weirdo.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:04.14,1:04:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其实她蛮骚的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's pretty hot.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:07.52,1:04:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你不陪她看电影\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then why not go out with her?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:09.73,1:04:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不喜欢她的声音\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't like her voice.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:11.86,1:04:13.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢女人的声音喔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I like women's voices...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:14.53,1:04:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很低沉的那一种\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}deep and low.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:16.28,1:04:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不一定啦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, actually it depends.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:19.20,1:04:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正就是听了以后 心跳会很快很快的那一种\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What I mean is, I like voices that make my heart beat faster.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:24.66,1:04:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你呢 你喜欢女孩子什么声音啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What about you? What kind of woman's voice do you like?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:29.13,1:04:30.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无所谓 喜欢就好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't really care.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:49.31,1:04:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,累了就回去睡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go home if you're tired.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:51.52,1:04:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会啊 我在听那两个人讲话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, I'm listening to those guys talking.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:57.07,1:04:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么远你也听得到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}From this far away?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:58.91,1:05:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还好啦 不懂得他们在讲什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not sure what they're saying
Dialogue: 0,1:05:02.12,1:05:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下就会打架了吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but they're gonna fight.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:08.29,1:05:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的耳朵好厉害喎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You have really good hearing.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:11.13,1:05:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能习惯了吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's a habit of mine.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:14.55,1:05:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我小时候眼睛生病 看不见东西都用耳朵在听\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I had bad eyes as a kid. I couldn't see well, so I listened.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:18.51,1:05:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,后来花很多钱把眼睛医好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My family spent a lot to fix my sight,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:21.39,1:05:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是习惯就改不掉啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but old habits die hard.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:24.31,1:05:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有的时候我觉得\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sometimes I think
Dialogue: 0,1:05:26.02,1:05:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,耳朵比眼睛还重要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}ears are more important than eyes.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:28.02,1:05:31.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很多东西用耳朵听比用眼睛看好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You "see" better with your ears.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:32.94,1:05:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就好像一个人很不开心会装得很开心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You can act happy...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:36.99,1:05:38.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是声音就装不了啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but your voice reveals the truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:39.53,1:05:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仔细一听就知道了嘛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Listen closely and you can tell.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:42.74,1:05:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Really?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:45.20,1:05:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像你的声音啊 现在就很不开心啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just like your voice now tells me you're not happy.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:49.96,1:05:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知不知道后面那两个人在说什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So what are they saying over there?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:53.38,1:05:54.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我试一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let me try.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:06.06,1:06:08.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好耶\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Goal!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:14.90,1:06:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三块\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Three bucks!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:20.70,1:06:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小张\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Chang!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:24.37,1:06:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-钱都收了 -五块\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-How much did we win? -Five bucks.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:29.96,1:06:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你两块\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Two for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:31.58,1:06:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我两块你三块\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why do you get three?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:33.42,1:06:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 那你三块\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay, three for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:34.88,1:06:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,整班人一起 我发觉小张的声音最大\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Chang had the liveliest voice amongst us.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:37.67,1:06:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下午在小巷踢球我觉得很热\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It got pretty hot playing soccer in the alley.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:40.13,1:06:43.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那年的夏天过得好快\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That summer went by very fast.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:56.08,1:07:59.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来来来干一杯 谢谢你的照顾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A toast to friendship. Thanks for everything.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:00.67,1:08:02.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,储够钱了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You saved up enough?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:02.63,1:08:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-对呀 -恭喜了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Yeah. -Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:10.64,1:08:11.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟着去哪里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where are you going next?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:11.93,1:08:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,往南走啊去一个叫Ushuaia的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}South to Ushuaia.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:18.19,1:08:19.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很冷的喎去那边干嘛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's cold there. Why do you want to go?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:21.86,1:08:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听说那边是世界尽头所以想去看一看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They say it's the end of the world. I'd like to see it.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:25.82,1:08:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你去过没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You ever been there?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:30.20,1:08:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听人说那儿有个灯塔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I heard there's a lighthouse down there.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:33.12,1:08:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很多失恋的人都喜欢去那边\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}People who are heartbroken go there...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:37.92,1:08:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说可以把不开心的东西留下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to leave their sadness behind.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:41.71,1:08:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在还有没有人这样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do people still do that?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:43.34,1:08:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道呢 有吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:54.68,1:08:56.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讲几句话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Say something.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:58.06,1:08:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:00.23,1:09:02.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是我这边唯一的朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're my only friend here.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:03.23,1:09:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,留个纪念嘛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It'll be a memento.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:04.53,1:09:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不喜欢拍照\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't like pictures.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:07.95,1:09:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-不知道说什么 -随便啦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't know what to say. Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:11.62,1:09:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么都可以讲心里面的话就可以\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Anything from the heart.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:14.83,1:09:16.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不开心也可以讲嘛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Even something sad.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:16.25,1:09:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以帮你留在世界的尽头\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll take it to the end of the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:18.04,1:09:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我没有不开心 -那就讲开心的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-I am not sad. -Something cheerful then.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:22.84,1:09:26.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啦你自己讲 我去玩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right, you go ahead. I'm gonna dance.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:16.43,1:10:17.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:18.27,1:10:19.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不要送你上去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Want me to help you upstairs?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:22.10,1:10:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm all right.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:23.73,1:10:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的可以吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You sure?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:26.73,1:10:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你走先吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You go on now.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:28.28,1:10:29.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我走了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Goodbye then.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:31.20,1:10:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你自己照顾你自己\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Take care of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:33.99,1:10:35.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望有机会可以再见到你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I hope we'll meet again someday.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:37.37,1:10:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你闭上眼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Close your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:39.50,1:10:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-干嘛 -闭上眼先\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Why? -Close your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:44.67,1:10:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你知不知道你很像一个人 -谁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-You know who you look like? -Who?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:47.55,1:10:49.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,盲侠\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The blind swordsman.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:49.97,1:10:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开玩笑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Very funny.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:52.68,1:10:53.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玩得开心点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Have fun.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:58.26,1:13:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以前我不喜欢去公厕找人 因为嫌脏\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I never used to pick up men in filthy public toilets.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:01.22,1:13:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最近久不久都会去一下 贪那边够方便\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}These days I do. It's convenient.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:04.77,1:13:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想不到会在那边碰上何宝荣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I didn't think I'd see Po-Wing there.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:06.98,1:13:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之后我就没再去过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've never gone back since.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:24.16,1:13:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都以为我跟何宝荣很不同\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I always thought I was different from Po-Wing.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:27.12,1:13:30.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎知道原来寂寞起来的时候 个个都一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Turns out lonely people are all the same.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:04.14,1:15:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在离开香港之前 我从公司拿走一笔钱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Before I left Hong Kong, I stole some money from work.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:07.72,1:15:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这份工作是我父亲介绍的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My father got me that job.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:10.23,1:15:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老板是他的好朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The boss was an old friend of his.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:12.77,1:15:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来了阿根廷这么久我不停在工作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've been working nonstop since I got here.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:15.44,1:15:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很想有一天能将钱还给人家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Someday I want to return the money
Dialogue: 0,1:15:18.40,1:15:20.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亦很想跟父亲说声对不起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and apologize to my father.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:39.34,1:15:41.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 爸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hello? Dad?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:43.63,1:15:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿辉啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is Fai.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:12.83,1:16:14.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿根廷十二月还是好热\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}December in Argentina is very hot.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:15.46,1:16:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那天我不用上班\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's my day off
Dialogue: 0,1:16:17.83,1:16:19.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很想着写张圣诞卡给他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I started writing my father a Christmas card,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:20.38,1:16:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么知道越写越长\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but it turned into a long letter.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:22.76,1:16:24.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除了对不起之外\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Apart from saying sorry,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:24.30,1:16:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还讲了好多他一直想知道 但又不敢问的事情\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I told him things he'd been afraid to ask about.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:29.97,1:16:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我希望他可以当我是个朋友 给我由头来过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I hoped he'd treat me as a friend and give me a chance to start over.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:27.36,1:17:31.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些臭猪真重\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Those damn pigs are breaking my back.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:31.83,1:17:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,累死我了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sick and tired of this.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:39.21,1:17:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为想赚多些钱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To boost my income,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:41.29,1:17:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去了屠房那边工作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've started working in a slaughterhouse.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:42.88,1:17:44.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除了工钱高之外\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The pay's much better
Dialogue: 0,1:17:44.42,1:17:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,时间也都很适合我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and the hours suit me fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:46.05,1:17:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚上开工白天睡觉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Work all night, sleep all day.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:48.72,1:17:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我开始跟回香港时间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm back on Hong Kong time.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:14.08,1:18:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 我啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hello? It's me.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:16.54,1:18:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没多久何宝荣又打电话来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Po-Wing called soon after.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:18.75,1:18:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他藉口说要拿回护照\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}His excuse was he wanted his passport back.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:21.12,1:18:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其实我也想给回他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I didn't mind returning it.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:23.29,1:18:25.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我不想跟他见面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I just didn't want to see him.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:25.67,1:18:27.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我怕听到他那句口头禅\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I dreaded hearing what he always says.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:07.63,1:19:09.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最近我又开始睡不着觉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm having trouble sleeping again.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:09.92,1:19:12.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那早看电视我才发觉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Watching TV that morning I realized
Dialogue: 0,1:19:12.68,1:19:14.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来香港跟阿根廷在地球的两边\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that Hong Kong and Argentina are on opposite sides of the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:15.18,1:19:17.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不晓得倒转的香港会是什么样子呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wonder how Hong Kong looks upside down.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:17.97,1:19:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可以表达你的感受或意见\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...you can express your feelings or opinions.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:22.14,1:19:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你最近很忙吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Have you been busy lately?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:23.31,1:19:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,东北风 2 级 汕头 东南风 2 级\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Northeast wind, grade 2. Shantou, south-southeast wind, grade 2.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:31.07,1:19:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,商业一台\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Commercial 1...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:32.15,1:19:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,逮捕了两名男子以跟进调查\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...arrested two men to facilitate the investigation.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:35.57,1:19:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,警方认为\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The police believe that...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:44.67,1:19:46.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为不想留在家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Since I don't want to stay at home,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:47.04,1:19:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以很多时候假期我也会回屠房开工\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I work overtime at the slaughterhouse.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:49.55,1:19:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我必须要承认何宝荣那句话是很有杀伤力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Po-Wing's words still get to me,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:53.01,1:19:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我真不想再继续下去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but this time I won't let them hurt me.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:25.67,1:20:26.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:27.54,1:20:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:28.63,1:20:32.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 阿辉没在这儿住了 他搬走了 拜拜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, Fai doesn't live here anymore. He moved. Bye.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:41.06,1:20:42.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很快就储够钱回香港\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I soon saved enough to go home.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:44.06,1:20:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在离开阿根廷之前\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Before I left Argentina
Dialogue: 0,1:20:45.56,1:20:47.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我决定再去瀑布一次\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I decided to try to see the falls again.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:07.88,1:26:10.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然兜兜转转走了很多冤枉路\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I lost my way and wandered around for a while...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:10.72,1:26:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我终于来到Iguazu\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but I finally reached Iguazu.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:13.26,1:26:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那天我很难过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I felt very sad.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:15.39,1:26:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我始终都觉得 站在瀑布下面的应该有两个人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I always thought there should be two of us standing here.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:43.16,1:28:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一九九七年一月\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's January 1997.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:45.00,1:28:46.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我终于来到世界的尽头\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I finally arrive at the end of the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:47.08,1:28:50.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里是美洲大陆南面的最后一个灯塔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is the southernmost lighthouse in South America.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:50.42,1:28:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再过去就是南极\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Beyond this is the South Pole.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:53.46,1:28:55.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,突然之间我很想回家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Suddenly I feel like going home.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:00.05,1:29:02.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我答应过阿辉把他的不开心留在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I promised Fai I'd leave his sadness here.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:03.93,1:29:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道那天晚上他讲过什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't know what he said that night.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:06.77,1:29:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能是录音机坏了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe the recorder broke
Dialogue: 0,1:29:09.10,1:29:10.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么声音都没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can't hear anything on the tape.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:10.61,1:29:13.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有两下很奇怪的声音\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just some strange noises...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:13.65,1:29:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像一个人在哭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}like someone sobbing.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:03.53,1:30:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我回台湾之前的一个晚上 我又回到布宜洛斯艾利斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I return to Buenos Aires the night before leaving for Taiwan.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:09.46,1:30:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很想跟阿辉说声再见\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I want to say goodbye to Fai,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:11.67,1:30:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过没有人知道他去了哪里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but nobody knows where he is.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:27.73,1:30:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,离开的时候天开始亮\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Dawn is breaking as I leave.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:29.94,1:30:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,台北现在应该是晚上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It must be night in Taipei.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:32.27,1:30:35.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道辽宁街的夜市开了没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wonder if the Liao Ning night market has started.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:40.11,1:30:41.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,中共中央领导人邓小平\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Chinese leader Deng Xiaoping
Dialogue: 0,1:30:41.78,1:30:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是在昨天晚上九点零八分病逝在北京三零一医院\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}died last night in a Beijing hospital.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:46.24,1:30:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,享年九十三岁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He was 93.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:48.00,1:30:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,中共中央电视台直到今天凌晨才发布邓小平的死讯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The announcement was made by PRC Central TV early this morning.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:52.63,1:30:54.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在台北起床已经是下午\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's afternoon when I wake up in Taipei.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:55.04,1:30:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在一九九七年二月二十日 我回到地球这一边\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's February 20, 1997. I'm back on this side of the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:18.82,1:31:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,过来尝尝我们的肉丸很好吃\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Good food here.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:29.66,1:31:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你要吃什么 -有什么好吃的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-What'll it be? -What's good?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:32.92,1:31:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,招牌面还有米糕臭豆腐都很好吃\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Our special meatballs, sticky rice and fried tofu are all tasty.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:40.17,1:31:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你要点什么 -点了 点过了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-What'll you have? -I've ordered already.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:43.38,1:31:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,米糕一碗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}One sticky rice.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:45.47,1:31:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们的东西不要钱啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You have to pay for that!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:47.43,1:31:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看你就要人家的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I bought this somewhere else, okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:49.26,1:31:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啦 去那边啦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hush! Leave the customer alone!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:52.10,1:31:54.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你不要吃嘛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Eat it and shut up!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:55.06,1:31:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我买了我付了钱耶\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is this how you treat customers?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:56.65,1:32:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,干什么啦 走开啦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's your problem? Leave him alone.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:01.49,1:32:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神经病 去那边\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're crazy! Get back to work!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:04.20,1:32:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,汤要吗 好 马上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}More soup? Right away.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:06.12,1:32:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,两位美女进去坐 里边坐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Please sit down. Special dumplings and sticky rice.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:15.50,1:32:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-请问有没有电话 -有电话在后面你从那边走过去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Do you have a phone? -Over there. Come around.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:18.67,1:32:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我回香港之前 我在台北停了一晚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I stayed in Taipei before returning to Hong Kong.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:21.38,1:32:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我走了去辽宁街 那晚那边很热闹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I visited the Liao Ning night market. It was very lively.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:25.26,1:32:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我见不到小张 我见到他的家人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I didn't see Chang, but I saw his family.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:47.87,1:32:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,离开时我拿了他一张相片 因为我不知道要等到几时才会再见到他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I took Chang's picture because I didn't know when I'd see him again.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:52.87,1:32:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我可以肯定 如果我想见他的话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What I do know is... if I want to see him...
Dialogue: 0,1:32:56.25,1:32:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,起码我知道在哪儿可以找到他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know where to find him.

